# Binder Placeholder Generator (project)

Flask + ReportLab app: upload CSV, customise header colours, download **A4 PDF** with **9 cards/page** (3×3), **63×88 mm** each, crop marks. No database or external APIs.

| Doc | Purpose |
|-----|---------|
| `README.md` | Quick start, CSV shape, print settings |
| `GUIDE.md` | Full user guide, rarity/type tables, limitations |
| `CURSOR.md` | **Authoritative** technical spec: coordinates, constants, functions, known PDF vs JSX limits |
| `REFERENCE.md` | Printable UI parity checklist vs `printed_ui.png` |

When changing **PDF output**, follow `.cursor/rules/binder-placeholder-pdf.mdc` and `CURSOR.md`. Goal: match **`printed_ui.png`** for spacing, fonts (within ReportLab limits), colours, and structure.
